articles.title: Sustained wet–dry cycling on early Mars - Nature.com
articles.description: Observations by the Curiosity rover at Gale Crater on Mars indicate that high-frequency wet–dry cycling occurred on the early Martian surface, indicating a possible seasonal climate conducive to prebiotic evolution on early Mars.

articles.title: Forty-one feared dead in migrant shipwreck in central Mediterranean - Reuters
articles.description: Italian authorities on Wednesday said forty-one migrants are thought to have died in a shipwreck last week in the central Mediterranean, according to accounts by survivors who have been taken to the island of Lampedusa.
